====================================================================

LaTeX Source Code
-----------------

This directory contains the LaTeX source code for:

  Kawchak K. National MCP Servers for Physical AI Oncology Clinical
  Trial Systems. Zenodo. 2026; 10.5281/zenodo.18916731.

