-----

  National_MCP_Servers_for_Physical_AI_Oncology_Clinical_Trial_Systems.tex
      Main LaTeX document (20 pages)

  arxiv.sty
      Modified arxiv-style template (kourgeorge/arxiv-style)
      Modifications: removed "A Preprint" header and subtitle

  references.bib
      BibTeX bibliography file with all references

  README
      This file

